#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:4
msgid "Hook Modifier"
msgstr "钩挂修改器--knight翻译"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:6
msgid ""
"The Hook modifier is used to deform a *Mesh*, *Curve* a *Lattice* using "
"another object (usually an *Empty* or a *Bone* but it can be any object)."
msgstr "牵引修改器用其他物体（通常是空物体或骨头，但可以用任何物体）来对变形*网格*、*弯曲**晶格*。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:9
msgid ""
"As the hook moves, it pulls vertices from the mesh with it. You can think"
" of it as animated :doc:`proportional editing "
"</editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/proportional_edit>`."
msgstr ""
"当钩移动时，它从它与网格拉扯顶点。你可以把它作为动画 :doc:`比例化编辑 "
"</editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/proportional_edit>` 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:13
msgid ""
"While hooks do not give you the fine control over vertices movement that "
"shape keys do, they have the advantage that you can grab vertices "
"directly for manipulation."
msgstr "在顶点运动方面，虽然牵引操作不能提供像形变键一样好的可控性，但是它有着可以直接抓取顶点操作的优势。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:18
msgid "Two spheres used as Hooks to deform a subdivided cube."
msgstr "两个用作牵引的球变形一个细分过的立方体。"

