#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:64
msgid ""
"The hook modifier stores vertex indices from the original mesh to "
"determine what to effect; this means that modifiers that generate "
"geometry, like subsurf, should always be applied **after** the hook "
"modifier; otherwise the generated geometry will be left out of the hook's"
" influence."
msgstr "牵引修改器保存了来自原始网格的顶点索引以确定影响哪些顶点；这意味着，产生新的几何形状的修改器（例如细分修改器），应该在牵引修改器之后应用；否则产生的几何形状将不会受牵引操作的影响。"

